    "gp_section_625522682226016939": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "4b732cd409480f4ae49bbcf9f369e401fdf2c827c45c342406bd6b7a11da9ad2_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggQ0Wtpv_Ah_label": "<p>TRY IT RISK-FREE – TODAY AT 50% OFF!</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_0": "<p>How does the personalization work?</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_1": "<p>Can I use any pet?</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_2": "<p>What kind of photo should I upload?</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_3": "<p>Will the background of my photo be kept?</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_4": "<p>Can I add more than one pet?</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_5": "<p>Will the shirt really look like my pet?</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_6": "<p>Does the print last after washing?</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_7": "<p>How do I choose the right size?</p>",
        "ggR2-nH2eM0_childItem_8": "<p>Is this a good gift idea?</p>",
        "ggRO0x1JBf5_text": "<p>It’s simple. Choose your size, select your shirt style, and upload a clear photo of your pet. Our team will then turn your pet’s photo into a unique design printed directly onto the shirt.</p>",
        "ggX2EniVm9q_text": "FAQ",
        "ggXHYiMjwOM_text": "<p>Yes. You can use a dog, cat, rabbit, or any other pet. As long as the photo is clear enough, we can use it.</p>",
        "gggxLjRu8yN_text": "<p>For the best result, upload a photo where your pet’s face is clearly visible, well-lit, and not covered by objects. A front-facing photo usually works best.</p>",
        "ggkDSqjyiH9_text": "<p>Yes, you can add multiple pets. We’ll adjust the design so each pet is clearly visible and nicely placed on the shirt.</p>",
        "ggkYAJ7acNt_text": "<p>Yes, the print is made to last. To keep the colors looking fresh, we recommend washing the shirt inside out in cold water and avoiding high-heat drying.</p>",
        "ggky6O4Xf0W_text": "<p>Yes, it’s a very personal and fun gift for birthdays, Father’s Day, Christmas, vacations, or anyone who loves their pet.</p>",
        "ggmkvDRWsjL_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>45-day</strong></span> money&nbsp;-back guarantee</p>",
        "ggmq1-tTmo__text": "<p>Please check the size guide before ordering. If you prefer a relaxed or oversized fit, we recommend choosing one size up.</p>",
        "ggoQB6YO3wQ_text": "<p>Yes. The design is created from the photo you upload. The clearer the photo, the more accurate and detailed the final result will be.</p>",
        "ggrxGymrlkU_text": "<p>No. We usually remove the background and keep only your pet, so it blends naturally into the tropical shirt design.</p>",
        "ggvyreBNINt_text": "<p>Still have questions ? Check here</p>",
        "ggxet32tdWW_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#00237E;\"><strong>free returns</strong></span><strong>,</strong> NO QUESTIONS ASKED&nbsp;</p>"
      },
